{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01FJg5Jo2KRxJ8qLXajUTqw5","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# RNG Utopia Workspace\n     2→\n     3→**Project handoff workspace for AI-assisted development**\n     4→\n     5→---\n     6→\n     7→## Structure\n     8→\n     9→This workspace contains:\n    10→\n    11→- **`sources/rng-utopia/`** - Active codebase (git submodule pointing to https://github.com/Rng-Utopia/rng-utopia)\n    12→- **`docs/`** - Project-level context for AI-assisted development\n    13→- **`scripts/`** - Verification and utility scripts\n    14→- **`CLAUDE.md` and `.cursor/rules/`** - AI behavior rules and project context\n    15→\n    16→---\n    17→\n    18→## Quick Start\n    19→\n    20→1. **Read project context**: See `docs/CONTEXT.md`\n    21→2. **Understand scope**: See `docs/SCOPE.md`\n    22→3. **Verify Setup**: Run `./scripts/verify` (The single command that proves it works)\n    23→4. **Work in codebase**: `sources/rng-utopia/`\n    24→\n    25→---\n    26→\n    27→## For AI Assistants (Workflow)\n    28→\n    29→**Core Principle: \"No proof = not done.\"**\n    30→\n    31→1. **Before Starting**: Check `docs/SCOPE.md`.\n    32→2. **During Work**: Follow \"Contract First\" - identify mocks/specs.\n    33→3. **Before Finishing**: \n    34→   - Run `./scripts/verify`\n    35→   - Include the **Completion Report** with proof in your final message.\n    36→\n    37→---\n    38→\n    39→## Git Structure\n    40→\n    41→- **Root repo**: Project management / meta repo (this workspace)\n    42→- **Submodule**: `sources/rng-utopia/` → https://github.com/Rng-Utopia/rng-utopia\n    43→\n    44→To update submodule:\n    45→```bash\n    46→cd sources/rng-utopia\n    47→git pull\n    48→cd ../..\n    49→git add sources/rng-utopia\n    50→git commit -m \"Update submodule\"\n    51→```\n    52→\n    53→---\n    54→\n    55→## Entry Points\n    56→\n    57→- **Context**: `docs/CONTEXT.md`\n    58→- **Scope**: `docs/SCOPE.md`\n    59→- **Decisions**: `docs/DECISIONS.md`\n    60→- **Verification**: `./scripts/verify`\n    61→- **Frontend runtime entrypoint**: `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/`\n    62→\n    63→### Frontend Structure Note\n    64→- `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/` is the deployed FE shell and current runtime entrypoint.\n    65→- Other folders under `sources/rng-utopia/apps/` are game-specific app scaffolds and may be incomplete.\n    66→\n    67→---\n    68→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_013FAwfsoCjZigwnK2PXyARE","session_id":"f4281aa2-334c-41cb-8346-1f9da2569415","uuid":"e0753fb5-a8c0-40f2-afc5-eac98ad0b172"}
