as a missing dependency: 'handleClose'. Either include it or remove the dependency array  react-hooks/exhaustive-deps\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/boss-raid/utils/mock-simulation.ts\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   432:5  warning  Unexpected console statement. Only these console methods are allowed: warn, error  no-console\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/components/CandlestickChart.tsx\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   50:9  warning  The 'historyCandles' conditional could make the dependencies of useEffect Hook (at line 208) change on every render. Move it inside the useEffect callback. Alternatively, wrap the initialization of 'historyCandles' in its own useMemo() Hook  react-hooks/exhaustive-deps\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/crypto-crash/context/CryptoCrashContext.tsx\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   212:6  warning  React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'currentTierRound'. Either include it or remove the dependency array  react-hooks/exhaustive-deps\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   238:6  warning  React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'currentTierRound'. Either include it or remove the dependency array  react-hooks/exhaustive-deps\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/components/WheelVisualization.tsx\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   360:6  warning  React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'getWinnerScrollPosition' and 'scrollPosition'. Either include them or remove the dependency array  react-hooks/exhaustive-deps\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/context/Lord